trans-unit.source: Provides trace event data specific to a thread and a process.
trans-unit.target: Fornece dados de evento de rastreamento específicos para um thread e um processo.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The TraceEventCache class, designed as a performance optimization for trace listener calls, is of interest only to developers creating custom trace listeners.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE]> A classe TraceEventCache, projetada como uma otimização de desempenho para chamadas de ouvinte de rastreamento, é interessante apenas para os desenvolvedores que criam ouvintes de rastreamento personalizada.

trans-unit.source: The TraceEventCache class is used as a parameter in tracing methods to accurately identify the source of a trace event.
trans-unit.target: A classe TraceEventCache é usada como um parâmetro em métodos de rastreamento para identificar com precisão a origem do evento de rastreamento.

trans-unit.source: Examples of methods that use TraceEventCache are <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceFilter.ShouldTrace%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Exemplos de métodos que usam TraceEventCache são <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>e <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceFilter.ShouldTrace%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceFilter.ShouldTrace%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache.LogicalOperationStack%2A> property contains data that can be used to correlate the trace with related traces.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache.LogicalOperationStack%2A>propriedade contém dados que podem ser usados para correlacionar o rastreamento com os rastreamentos relacionados.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache.LogicalOperationStack%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Gets the call stack for the current thread.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a pilha de chamadas do thread atual.

trans-unit.source: The Callstack property gets the call stack from the <xref:System.Environment.StackTrace%2A> property of the <xref:System.Environment> class.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade de pilha de chamadas obtém a pilha de chamadas da <xref:System.Environment.StackTrace%2A>propriedade de <xref:System.Environment>classe.</xref:System.Environment> </xref:System.Environment.StackTrace%2A>

trans-unit.source: The property value lists method calls in reverse chronological order.
trans-unit.target: O valor da propriedade listas chamadas de método em ordem cronológica inversa.

trans-unit.source: That is, the most recent method call is described first.
trans-unit.target: Ou seja, a chamada de método mais recente é descrita pela primeira vez.

trans-unit.source: One line of stack trace information is listed for each method call on the stack.
trans-unit.target: Uma linha de informações de rastreamento de pilha é listada para cada chamada de método na pilha.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Environment.StackTrace%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte <xref:System.Environment.StackTrace%2A>.</xref:System.Environment.StackTrace%2A>

trans-unit.source: A string containing stack trace information.
trans-unit.target: Uma cadeia de caracteres que contém informações de rastreamento de pilha.

trans-unit.source: This value can be an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Esse valor pode ser uma cadeia de caracteres vazia ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets the date and time at which the event trace occurred.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a data e a hora em que o rastreamento de evento ocorreu.

trans-unit.source: The first time the property is accessed in an instance of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache> class, the current time is returned.
trans-unit.target: Na primeira vez em que a propriedade é acessada em uma instância do <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache>classe atual é retornada.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache>

trans-unit.source: Subsequent queries of this property in that instance return that same <xref:System.DateTime> value, allowing it to be used as a timestamp.
trans-unit.target: Mesmas que as consultas subsequentes dessa propriedade nessa instância retornam <xref:System.DateTime>valor, permitindo que ele seja usado como um carimbo de hora.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.DateTime> structure whose value is a date and time expressed in Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.DateTime>estrutura cujo valor é uma data e hora, expressada em tempo Universal Coordenado (UTC).</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: Gets the correlation data, contained in a stack.
trans-unit.target: Obtém os dados de correlação, contidos em uma pilha.

trans-unit.source: The correlation data is stored as an object in the call context with the name "System.Diagnostics.Trace.CorrelationManagerSlot".
trans-unit.target: Os dados de correlação são armazenados como um objeto no contexto da chamada com o nome "System.Diagnostics.Trace.CorrelationManagerSlot".

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager> class provides methods used to store a logical operation identity in a thread-bound context and automatically tag each trace event generated by the thread with the stored identity.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager>classe fornece métodos usados para armazenar uma identidade de operação lógica em um contexto de thread associado e identificar automaticamente a cada evento de rastreamento gerado pelo thread com a identidade armazenada.</xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager> is accessed through the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.CorrelationManager%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager>é acessada por meio de <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.CorrelationManager%2A?displayProperty=fullName>propriedade.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.CorrelationManager%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager>

trans-unit.source: Each call to the <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.StartLogicalOperation%2A> method pushes a new logical operation identity onto the stack.
trans-unit.target: Cada chamada para o <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.StartLogicalOperation%2A>método envia uma nova identidade da operação lógica para a pilha.</xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.StartLogicalOperation%2A>

trans-unit.source: Each call to the <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.StopLogicalOperation%2A> method pops a logical operation identity from the stack
trans-unit.target: Cada chamada para o <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.StopLogicalOperation%2A>método aparece uma identidade de operação lógica da pilha</xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.StopLogicalOperation%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Collections.Stack"></xref> containing correlation data.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Collections.Stack"> </xref> que contém dados de correlação.

trans-unit.source: Gets the unique identifier of the current process.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o identificador exclusivo do processo atual.

trans-unit.source: Until the process terminates, the process identifier uniquely identifies the process throughout the system.
trans-unit.target: Até que o processo termina, o identificador de processo identifica exclusivamente o processo em todo o sistema.

trans-unit.source: The system-generated unique identifier of the current process.
trans-unit.target: O identificador exclusivo gerado pelo sistema do processo atual.

trans-unit.source: Gets a unique identifier for the current managed thread.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um identificador exclusivo para o thread gerenciado atual.

trans-unit.source: The thread identifier is the value of the <xref:System.Threading.Thread.ManagedThreadId%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property formatted as a string.
trans-unit.target: O identificador de thread é o valor da <xref:System.Threading.Thread.ManagedThreadId%2A?displayProperty=fullName>propriedade formatada como uma cadeia de caracteres.</xref:System.Threading.Thread.ManagedThreadId%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A string that represents a unique integer identifier for this managed thread.
trans-unit.target: Uma cadeia de caracteres que representa o identificador inteiro exclusivo para esse thread gerenciado.

trans-unit.source: Gets the current number of ticks in the timer mechanism.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o número atual de tiques no mecanismo de temporizador.

trans-unit.source: The get accessor calls the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to get the timestamp.
trans-unit.target: As chamadas de acessador get o <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A?displayProperty=fullName>método para obter o carimbo de hora.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch> class uses a high-resolution performance counter, <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A> returns the current value of that counter.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch>classe usa um contador de desempenho de alta resolução, <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A>retorna o valor atual do contador.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch> class uses the system timer, <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A> returns the <xref:System.DateTime.Ticks%2A> property of <xref:System.DateTime.Now%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Se a <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch>classe usa o timer do sistema, <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A>retorna a <xref:System.DateTime.Ticks%2A>propriedade de <xref:System.DateTime.Now%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.DateTime.Now%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.DateTime.Ticks%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch>

trans-unit.source: The tick counter value of the underlying timer mechanism.
trans-unit.target: O valor do contador de escala do mecanismo de temporizador subjacente.
